<p><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipient's copy ]">RC</abbr> (<span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Library of Congress ]">DLC</span>).</p></div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#TSJN-01-07-0373-fn-0001-ptr" id="TSJN-01-07-0373-fn-0001">1</a>
<p>This and the following words in italics are written in code and were decoded by TJ interlineally. For TJs difficulty in decoding the letter see his letter to Monroe of 14 Jan. 1785, in which he acknowledges its receipt. His decoding has been verified by the editors, employing Code No. 5.</p></div>
